{
  "texts": [
    "Large Language Models perform best under clear, exact instructions.",
    "\"Summary of this product review,\" for example, is more successful than \"What is your opinion on this?\"",
    "Structure helps the model to follow a rational development.",
    "Consult templates, numbered lists, or bullet points.",
    "For instance, asking the model to provide the outcome in a certain tone such as formal or friendly or as a JSON object gives necessary structure.Constraints serve as model guiding values."
  ]
}